{"tid":922931,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"小明突然發覺自已失戀","createTime":"2018-11-30T19:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T20:59:32.000Z","uid":43751,"like":148,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9d84f25688d8ab54a9c178fa368936ffcead1b","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"小明把朋友約出<br />\n朋友說你賤<br />\n小明答我賤<br />\n小明把三五杯酒吞下<br />\n半個雞煲<br />\n多醉<br />\n在這刻 傷"},{"pid":"94c40b2eb115c0e1692c464ff69d738b62a142c5","tid":922931,"uid":201303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:27:52.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"25c295ad4886e14e49df902db95af7838e5c9cbe","tid":922931,"uid":2706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:28:35.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"3922f26087844df8819574c045e4a789705e30b0","tid":922931,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:30:45.000Z","msg":"小明！"},{"pid":"0d164bb2137ccef79dfe5376eb5a2ffa175ac490","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:32:15.000Z","msg":"朋友們<br />\n雞煲<br />\n藍妹啤酒<br />\n萬事發檸檬香煙<br />\n嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n一日晚過<br />\n<br />\n朋友說：叫你真誠愛人<br />\n小明答：我不、像風一樣自由<br />\n<br />\n小明小便<br />\n在便廁<br />\n隔離的人 <br />\n不知沖水 或尿回彈<br />\n彈濕小明<br />\n尿廁上有半個拋下的煙咀<br />\n<br />\n小明回到朋友的酒局<br />\n喝了半杯<br />\n因為被廁的尿濺濕"},{"pid":"0e8390929a9eff3bf67867d72be2e45a8b020a88","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:35:38.000Z","msg":"喝不少酒<br />\n小明被傷了<br />\n<br />\n朋友說：早叫你真誠待人<br />\n小明沒有<br />\n朋友說：抵死<br />\n<br />\n又把半杯啤酒喝下<br />\n小明說 今天失戀 要不要往死飲"},{"pid":"e0db98ab75e00a5054fb7638b3e9228bce9177a2","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"小明不愛任何<br />\n但被嫌棄了<br />\n小明沒預算<br />\n<br />\n跟朋友 飲兩三杯啤酒<br />\n小明一個人 從鏡內發展恩愛<br />\n在一起會有多美"},{"pid":"1b8da94e577c5f76abbf3202a2b518b524632831","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"小明告訴自己<br />\n自由的<br />\n換一個<br />\n小明可以換一個<br />\n更高<br />\n高鼻高<br />\n更巨乳<br />\n<br />\n像林夕說：這此當對著 前度要她高舉姆指<br />\n失戀 <br />\n小明覺得要自信"},{"pid":"f3a86536205eba16c0daa38f4e8288a7cb14b72d","tid":922931,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽出故，逼人唔訓咁追文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6627edd5c7dfde948b491a5036d95c082fc1491b","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:45:53.000Z","msg":"喜歡不難<br />\n破處不難<br />\n相處很難 <br />\n小明像風一樣自由<br />\n<br />\n隨你<br />\n正如隨機播放<br />\n<br />\n除非你是我"},{"pid":"7c3a523fd3f2fe75ba1db01d5ae3052597fcb8dd","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"小明把任何人強吻<br />\n又被任何人拋棄<br />\n<br />\n小明告訴朋友：不要驚訝, 我是註定被拋棄<br />\n沒說話<br />\n小明把藍妹嚟酒狠吞<br />\n<br />\n又抽一根煙<br />\n又到公廁吐尿<br />\n像溝女失戀一樣<br />\n概定"},{"pid":"f9dac87e9ad59ced0bda3b47066c9ee050988b39","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:54:08.000Z","msg":"接吻<br />\n是小明把脷伸進對方的喉嚨<br />\n抑或 對方要吞小明的脷入胃？"},{"pid":"f9f9b524f86fc5114e576c34f89ad9dedfd10059","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"小明在避雨<br />\n天空有太陽 也有雨<br />\n在車站看見前度<br />\n突然大雨<br />\n沒話好說<br />\n吐<br />\n在工作什麼 小明問<br />\n沒聽入耳<br />\n<br />\n小明心想：這他媽的好陽光 下大雨 欠我嗎<br />\n尷尬<br />\n小明喜歡前度<br />\n但沒說<br />\n想抽一根煙<br />\n但對方不喜歡<br />\n<br />\n對方上了巴士<br />\n小明見雨和太陽之間 有彩虹<br />\n今年小明 沒有坐飛機"},{"pid":"a9d8c7bcadc56c78c7403c282511405449cf0261","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:59:51.000Z","msg":"還是告訴朋友 <br />\n小明<br />\n能不能住死飲"},{"pid":"ad33fe3b74d8e2a918379e1929c6af36bb739e19","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:03:28.000Z","msg":"小明問一個問題<br />\n對方說<br />\n喜歡過 但你值得我喜歡嗎<br />\n<br />\n小明把電話斷了<br />\n找喜歡的朋友 飲酒<br />\n天氣好 風冷 清涼<br />\n要誰 小明問<br />\n要一些啤酒<br />\n跟友人聊天<br />\n不是壞事"},{"pid":"ecdffd79b04ac8f98d1971082f5bb529eee84436","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:07:29.000Z","msg":"如果有願<br />\n小明是每天起床 工作 喝酒 睡<br />\n重覆<br />\n<br />\n上班不開心嗎<br />\n同事好 客人好<br />\n沒兒女私情多開心"},{"pid":"6a054425704aaf99b0727357b871f728f3606b40","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:10:30.000Z","msg":"朋友說 你看破紅塵嗎<br />\n小明沒有<br />\n小明要去中國西北<br />\n因為喜歡西空音樂<br />\n我像風一樣自由<br />\n<br />\n東北交了一個朋友<br />\n女的<br />\n小明想去一去<br />\n或多或少有情感"},{"pid":"02d2a6062557584813ab0341537aeb160b3861e6","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:11:51.000Z","msg":"我像風一樣自由<br />\n就像你的溫柔 不能挽留"},{"pid":"5826c02faddbf26ac8cc47737a56ff0e7c11a5ce","tid":922931,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:13:03.000Z","msg":"半夜三更出文叫人點捨得瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09aa5c3bcb55da844b8b4cb1a75abbad8605d914","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:13:53.000Z","msg":"天氣是李清照的天氣<br />\n叫人不醉嗎"},{"pid":"acb3d321dd37e34d7a61bc54878d5a7ba2c0fdf2","tid":922931,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9249e751e345ffa9d158271ab4d7089d557530","tid":922931,"uid":68375,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:15:20.000Z","msg":"小明好似變了"},{"pid":"b70e654d3e96ec42ef2d3063a1099d17a901d7eb","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:18:56.000Z","msg":"小明交兩個女友<br />\n討厭小明抽煙<br />\n又交了兩個 抽煙的中學生<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n小明還是一個一抽煙<br />\n把煙吐入月球<br />\n夜靜<br />\n街燈橙黃<br />\n不說喜歡討厭<br />\n看穿霧煙<br />\n看小明一個人在抽煙<br />\n<br />\n小明希望 有一頭狗伴自己"},{"pid":"457c71ce9e896ed8c63e3ba2b5ef4995541e5ff6","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:26:12.000Z","msg":"小明喜歡中國西北歌手許巍<br />\n雖然連登仔不喜歡大陸人 簡體字<br />\n但不關小明事<br />\n小明喜歡許巍<br />\n<br />\n社會要反 隨他<br />\n小明必要 選自己喜歡的<br />\n<br />\n這一輩字 喜歡 就選 <br />\n不介懷別人"},{"pid":"3ad178dff35f66e14840063e0bc734e20ac9c9ec","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"457c71ce9e896ed8c63e3ba2b5ef4995541e5ff6","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:26:12.000Z","msg":"小明喜歡中國西北歌手許巍<br />\n雖然連登仔不喜歡大陸人 簡體字<br />\n但不關小明事<br />\n小明喜歡許巍<br />\n<br />\n社會要反 隨他<br />\n小明必要 選自己喜歡的<br />\n<br />\n這一輩字 喜歡 就選 <br />\n不介懷別人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:26:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XZ5OfVUw2JM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXZ5OfVUw2JM&d=%2FrJA25CgA%2BBTVbOoZHtMgC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=aed0a731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XZ5OfVUw2JM</a>"},{"pid":"d86e9163d64a43e4f7a5f93218ad50d54e3c9ba7","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:41:45.000Z","msg":"小明面對失戀<br />\n只有一個方法<br />\n幻想一個另巨乳女 在吻自己的耳朵<br />\n如果被一個平胸女拋棄<br />\n就得性幻想另一個巨乳出現<br />\n樂觀嘛"},{"pid":"90fd74029942e205ebee4283e04eef0ab579b2c7","tid":922931,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:43:32.000Z","msg":"都係醉左睇卜大"},{"pid":"c3b968675d7a48c4a0e255fc995260d393a04088","tid":922931,"uid":208722,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:44:23.000Z","msg":"癡孖筋，自己攞嚟賤喺度叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbedde1cb9912c524d3b3f15fe13954b0d4e893","tid":922931,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTim